It is estimated 150 million people are [[homeless]] worldwide <ref>{{cite web|url=https://yaleglobal.yale.edu/content/cities-grow-worldwide-so-do-numbers-homeless}}</ref>. [[Habitat for Humanity]] estimated in 2015 that 1.6 billion people around the world live in "inadequate shelter".<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.habitat.org/getinv/events/world-habitat-day/housing-facts|title=World Habitat Day|publisher=}}</ref>
This is a list of countries (not all 195) by the homeless population present on any given night.
